title: Dr. Martens AW14 Film // #STANDFORSOMETHING
description:
Dr. Martens continues to celebrate free-thinking individuals; from the first timers to those who have been with us forever. The Spitfires, Alex, Lauren, Luna and Family Rain share what they stand for in this short film.

What do you stand for?
